<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2387] UIMA tests are unstable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2387</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The UIMA tests fail frequently in hudson now.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am not sure if this is due to not being able to connect to specific sites,&lt;br/&gt;
but if this is the case it would be better to use a Mock component instead&lt;br/&gt;
that doesn&apos;t need to do this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
